	<div  class="accordion-item__content">
					

<div  class="text">
            <p>The <a href="https://new.smith.edu/your-campus/offices-services/human-resources/benefits#retirement#financial">Retirement Plan Investment Committee </a>works with an investment or fiduciary advisory firm to establish Smiths internal governance procedures, and to select and monitor investment choices.</p>

      </div>
			</div>
</div>

              



	

<div  data-accordion-expanded="true" class="accordion-item js-accordion-item" id="safety-committee-for-research-and-instruction-10">
	

