	</h2>
	<div  class="accordion-item__content">
					

<div  class="text">
            <p>The colleges safety committees and inventory and regulatory affairs unit ensure a safe environment for students, employees, faculty and staff, as well as those visiting our facilities, and helps to ensure compliance with federal, state, and local codes and regulations.</p>

      </div>
			</div>
</div>

              



	

<div  data-accordion-expanded="true" class="accordion-item js-accordion-item" id="sherrerd-center-for-teaching-and-learning,-advisory-board-11">
	

