	<div  class="accordion-item__content">
					

<div  class="text">
            <p>The mission of the <a href="https://new.smith.edu/discover-smith/governance/staff-council">Staff Council </a>is to give members of the administrative, administrative support and service staff a focused and direct involvement in the governance of non-academic affairs and in the life of the Smith College community.</p>

      </div>
			</div>
</div>

              



	

<div  data-accordion-expanded="true" class="accordion-item js-accordion-item" id="student-government-association-13">
	

