				</button>

	</h2>
	<div  class="accordion-item__content">
					

<div  class="text">
            <p>The Committee on Study Abroad and a subcommittee on Junior Years Abroad meets to consider such matters as the chair or the subcommittees deem necessary. The Subcommittee on Junior Years Abroad holds an annual meeting with students from each of the preceding year's Junior Year Abroad programs.</p>

      </div>
			</div>
</div>

              



	

<div  data-accordion-expanded="true" class="accordion-item js-accordion-item" id="sustainability,-committee-on-15">
	

