				</button>

	</h2>
	<div  class="accordion-item__content">
					

<div  class="text">
            <p>The Committee on Sustainability is concerned with the best long-term use of finite natural resources and with the college's impact on the local, regional and global environment.</p>

      </div>
			</div>
</div>

              



	

<div  data-accordion-expanded="true" class="accordion-item js-accordion-item" id="tenure-and-promotion-16">
	

